settings.description: The first level from Super Mario Flash.
Dodge the bullets, Touch the snake Corners, and defeat Lemmy, He has more lives and resistance to fire than ever before. Good luck defeating Lemmy and finding the secret exit!
While in his usual trips, Mario encounters a Bullet Bill field, filled to the brim with Bullet and Missile Bills. What powers and quirks will Mario find in his adventure?
